the Florrick rehabilitation.

04:50.620 --> 04:51.939
(chuckling):
Oh, wow.

04:51.990 --> 04:54.481
Now I'm starting to feel
like a slacker.

04:54.520 --> 04:57.387
Eli is starting to clock
more billable hours than us.

04:57.430 --> 04:59.523
Who is it, one of the airlines?

04:59.560 --> 05:02.028
I heard a jet
went off the runway at O'Hare.

05:02.060 --> 05:04.324
No, but I might be able
to sign them.

05:04.370 --> 05:05.689
I can decide for both of us?

05:05.730 --> 05:07.391
Yes. Just keep me in the loop.

05:07.440 --> 05:08.691
Mm-hmm.

05:08.900 --> 05:10.868
Cheese.

05:12.740 --> 05:14.105
Cheese?

05:14.140 --> 05:17.576
Yes. We represent
the Wisconsin State Dairy Guild,

05:17.610 --> 05:19.475
and we need your help.

05:20.520 --> 05:22.784
With cheese?
Yes.

05:25.790 --> 05:29.351
A certain kind of cheese
or all cheese?

05:29.390 --> 05:30.857
There was an_ outbreak
of listeri05is

05:30.890 --> 05:32.528
