05:33.830 --> 05:35.525
News reports say
the outbreak

05:35.560 --> 05:38.427
was traced to bacterial-
infected cheese slices.

05:38.470 --> 05:39.664
Five children
are hospitalized,

05:39.700 --> 05:41.463
four teachers
are ill,

05:41.500 --> 05:43.104
and we're getting alarmed calls
from government officials.

05:45.710 --> 05:48.804
Does the guild have a contract
with an existing PR firm?

05:48.840 --> 05:49.738
Keyser & Associates.

05:49.780 --> 05:51.702
They're working
on an "Eat Cheese" campaign.

05:51.750 --> 05:53.809
Not anymore.
You hire me, I am one voice.

05:53.850 --> 05:55.670
Tell me if that's okay,
