05:55.720 --> 05:57.142
I'll have to get
permission.
That's fine for now,

05:57.190 --> 05:58.782
but I need someone here
who doesn't need

05:58.820 --> 05:59.787
to get permission.

05:59.820 --> 06:01.549
Agnes, hello.
Get... get me...

06:01.590 --> 06:02.682
Monthly retainer
of $60,000 a month.

06:02.730 --> 06:04.686
Hourly still applies.
You'll find that's competitive.

06:04.730 --> 06:06.459
Fine.
Get me everything

06:06.500 --> 06:07.853
on listeriosis,

06:07.900 --> 06:10.869
anyone who will speak
out against cheese.

06:10.900 --> 06:12.868
And I'll need more
investigator time. Get Kalinda.

06:12.900 --> 06:13.730
