...may also be tainted.

06:20.810 --> 06:21.731
It was just after recess.

06:21.780 --> 06:24.874
The culprit--
the most innocent of foods.

06:24.910 --> 06:26.741
Cheese.

06:26.780 --> 06:28.543
This cell phone video,
Oh, dear God.

06:28.580 --> 06:30.616
