Lockhart/Gardner

07:08.920 --> 07:09.682
as temporary counsel.

07:09.730 --> 07:12.153
NEWSCASTER:
...as we learn more.

07:12.190 --> 07:14.852
And get me the CEO
of Heather Farms--

07:14.900 --> 07:16.925
before he talks to a reporter.

07:19.000 --> 07:20.831
Here he comes now.

07:20.870 --> 07:22.030
You just tell him
what you told me.

07:22.070 --> 07:23.833
What's wrong?
Is everything all right?

07:23.870 --> 07:24.905
I don't know.

07:24.940 --> 07:27.807
I got a call from someone
at the Vindicator.

07:27.840 --> 07:30.502
She asked if I had an
opinion about the results

07:30.550 --> 07:32.916
of the medical investigation
of Dr. Farland.

07:32.950 --> 07:34.645
The...?
I don't understand.

07:34.680 --> 07:35.908
It's a year off.
I know.

07:35.950 --> 07:37.918
She said the FDA expedited it.

07:37.950 --> 07:40.783
She got an early look, and
they're siding with Dr. Farland.

07:40.820 --> 07:42.924
ALICIA:
It may not be true.

07:42.960 --> 07:44.120
It doesn't matter.

07:44.160 --> 07:45.787
Any rumor
of an investigation

07:45.830 --> 07:47.229
that goes
against us hurts us.

07:47.260 --> 07:49.251
Did this reporter say
when she wanted a comment?

07:49.300 --> 07:51.063
This afternoon.

07:51.100 --> 07:53.830
She has to go to press Monday
with the leak.

07:53.870 --> 07:54.996
Here's her number.

07:55.040 --> 07:56.928
She's the
Metroeditor.

07:56.970 --> 07:59.234
Kate Hanson-- I know her.
Let me give her a call.

07:59.270 --> 08:00.737
She'll be easy
to stall.

08:00.780 --> 08:02.839
Thank you for doing this.
(cooing)

08:02.880 --> 08:04.939
Once more around
the park.

08:04.980 --> 08:06.845
(baby fussing)

08:06.880 --> 08:08.575
(engine starting)

08:08.620 --> 08:09.882
So what do you think?

08:09.920 --> 08:11.979
I think we have
a gun to our head,

08:12.020 --> 08:12.850
and can't wait
for trial.

08:12.890 --> 08:14.949
We have to get a good deal
in mediation.

08:14.990 --> 08:16.526
Damn!
Be right there.

08:16.560 --> 08:18.949
Owen, can you do me a favor?

08:20.000 --> 08:21.888
Diane, we...

08:21.930 --> 08:23.727
I'll call you back.

08:25.030 --> 08:26.736
I think the mediator's
lying to us.

08:26.770 --> 08:28.692
I think you're right.

08:28.740 --> 08:30.002
Two hours
and a bottle of wine,

08:30.040 --> 08:31.769
we can settle this.

08:31.810 --> 08:34.131
Just this? Why not
the Middle East?

08:34.180 --> 08:37.809
It's game theory with
imperfect information, Will.

08:37.850 --> 08:39.977
Why don't we
make it perfect?

08:40.020 --> 08:41.908
I thought you
liked imperfect.

08:41.950 --> 08:44.680
Poker over chess.

08:46.120 --> 08:47.849
You sure you're on
the right floor?

08:47.890 --> 08:48.959
I'm serious.

08:48.990 --> 08:51.629
We used to settle a lot
of things in the old days.

08:51.660 --> 08:53.594
We used to unsettle
a lot of things, too.

08:53.630 --> 08:54.858
I'm going into my room now.

08:54.900 --> 08:57.027
You haven't heard our case yet.
It's a good one.

08:57.070 --> 08:58.992
Then I can't wait.
Good-bye, Celeste.

08:59.030 --> 09:01.260
My number.

09:01.300 --> 09:03.803
When you're ready
to negotiate.

09:07.210 --> 09:09.201
(elevator bell dings)

09:22.890 --> 09:25.120
The whole weekend?

09:25.160 --> 09:26.229
Maybe not the whole one.

09:26.260 --> 09:27.295
It's hot, right?
The nights are hot?

09:27.330 --> 09:29.321
Oh, steaming.

09:29.360 --> 09:33.933
Sultry with the scent
of jasmine, forbidden love.

09:33.970 --> 09:35.062
Coat, no coat?

09:35.100 --> 09:37.102
No coat.

09:37.140 --> 09:38.209
You're fine with this, right?

09:38.240 --> 09:40.231
I just need someone
with the kids through Sunday.

09:40.280 --> 09:41.975
Sure. The fun uncle.

09:42.010 --> 09:42.999
I'm the fun uncle.

09:43.050 --> 09:47.009
So you and Will
in a hotel room.

09:47.050 --> 09:48.369
Yes.

09:48.420 --> 09:51.139
Will, me, four lavwers,
six of their lawyers

09:51.190 --> 09:52.009
and a mediator.

09:52.050 --> 09:53.813
