out the hot tub.

09:53.860 --> 09:56.010
In a businessman's hotel.

09:56.060 --> 09:58.187
The best sex I ever had
was in a businessman's hotel.

09:58.230 --> 10:00.653
Oh, okay.
Can we not go there?

10:00.700 --> 10:02.122
(laughs)
You are so funny.

10:02.160 --> 10:05.323
You are the most prudish
wanton woman I know.

10:08.740 --> 10:10.230
Hey.

10:10.270 --> 10:12.067
What was that?

10:12.110 --> 10:13.372
What? Nothing.
I have to go.

10:13.410 --> 10:15.173
But you were about
to say something.

10:15.210 --> 10:17.405
You won't get in a fight
with Peter, right?

10:17.450 --> 10:19.270
He's picking up the kids
for dinner Saturday night.

10:19.310 --> 10:21.119
I didn't mean it--

10:21.150 --> 10:22.811
about the "wanton."

10:22.850 --> 10:24.909
Alicia, talk to me.

10:24.950 --> 10:26.349
Owen, I would if I had the time.

10:26.390 --> 10:28.051
You have to wait
for the elevator,

10:28.090 --> 10:30.058
so talk to me here.

10:30.090 --> 10:31.819
Okay.

10:31.860 --> 10:32.929
You're sleeping with Will,

10:32.960 --> 10:34.996
which is why you left
your husband.

10:35.030 --> 10:36.156
(elevator bell dings)

10:36.200 --> 10:37.963
Oh, come on.

10:38.000 --> 10:40.195
I'll call you later.

10:40.240 --> 10:41.298
(phone ringing)

10:41.340 --> 10:43.001
Gretchen Battista.

10:43.040 --> 10:45.008
No, Kate retired
three months ago.

10:45.040 --> 10:48.009
I'm her replacement, Mr....

10:48.040 --> 10:50.144
Gardner.

10:50.180 --> 10:52.171
Yeah, so you'll be
getting a package

10:52.210 --> 10:54.144
in about an hour or 50,
Ms. Battista.

10:54.180 --> 10:55.078
Just ignore it.

10:55.120 --> 10:57.088
Oh, I already got it.

10:57.120 --> 10:58.712
My parents drink Scotch.

10:58.750 --> 11:01.082
They'll be really grateful.

11:01.120 --> 11:02.348
And what might you need?

11:02.390 --> 11:04.028
You contacted my client
for comment

11:04.060 --> 11:05.254
on the FDA investigation.

11:05.290 --> 11:07.690
I thought I might help.

11:07.730 --> 11:09.823
You wouldn't happen to be
fishing for what I might know,

11:09.870 --> 11:10.825
would you, Mr. Gardner?

11:10.870 --> 11:12.326
I might be.

11:12.370 --> 11:14.167
I just find it odd that you'd be

11:14.200 --> 11:16.395
the only reporter
leaked an FDA decision.

11:16.440 --> 11:18.237
Maybe I'm just
a better reporter.

11:18.270 --> 11:20.135
