that's lying

11:20.180 --> 11:23.308
and trying to undermine
this negotiation.

11:23.350 --> 11:26.069
So come in for an interview,
and you can offer some context.

11:26.110 --> 11:28.772
Okay. How about lunch
on Monday?

11:28.820 --> 11:30.117
Oh, you mean after my deadline?

11:30.150 --> 11:31.947
Oh, I don't think so.

11:31.990 --> 11:33.719
How about in my office
in one hour?

11:33.760 --> 11:34.954
Two hours.

11:34.990 --> 11:36.082
(phone beeps)

11:36.120 --> 11:38.782
I thought we had agreed this
morning to lower your ask

11:38.830 --> 11:40.320
by $100,000.

11:40.360 --> 11:42.157
Yes, and we reevaluated
our position,

11:42.200 --> 11:44.065
and we're staying
with our original ask.

11:45.170 --> 11:47.161
(laughs)

11:47.200 --> 11:49.134
