your son, that he, Peter,

24:25.730 --> 24:27.789
was at fault for
you kicking him out

24:27.830 --> 24:29.593
'cause he slept
with somebody else,

24:29.630 --> 24:33.794
and so now I'm wondering
who that somebody else was.

24:34.640 --> 24:38.064
Zach told you this?
