bad at bluffing.

25:47.780 --> 25:50.669
Who's the
lady friend?

25:50.710 --> 25:52.678
The. . .?
The lawyer.

25:52.710 --> 25:55.144
I get a strong
possessive sense there.

25:56.180 --> 25:58.239
You're not
gang to say?

25:58.290 --> 26:00.850
