you'll use it in negotiations.

26:00.890 --> 26:02.755
(laughs)

26:05.290 --> 26:07.258
(sighs)

26:07.290 --> 26:08.757
Call.

26:12.870 --> 26:14.838
So how do you know
Gretchen?

26:14.870 --> 26:16.189
Gretchen?

26:16.240 --> 26:17.366
The reporter.

26:17.400 --> 26:19.231
Through your firm?

26:20.680 --> 26:22.636
