you're talking about.

26:22.680 --> 26:25.171
Hmm, so are we gonna play cards
all night

26:25.210 --> 26:26.302
or are we gonna negotiate?

26:26.350 --> 26:28.841
How about both?

26:28.880 --> 26:32.088
You lose this hand, you convince
your client to take my deal.

26:32.120 --> 26:36.682
