$500,000.

26:45.730 --> 26:48.267
So that's your bottom line,
huh, $10 million?

26:51.770 --> 26:53.829
I miss you, Will, I really do.

26:53.880 --> 26:56.769
Why did you
drop out?

26:56.810 --> 26:57.947
I didn't.

26:57.980 --> 26:59.106
Moved on.

26:59.150 --> 27:00.640
