pretty adult things ourselves.

27:08.420 --> 27:10.615
Come on, one bet.

27:11.460 --> 27:13.997
We settle this
like adults.

27:14.030 --> 27:16.328
No mediator.

27:16.360 --> 27:18.328
Your lady friend
will be so impressed

27:18.370 --> 27:22.238
