with $10 million in your hand.

27:23.840 --> 27:25.808
No, thanks.

27:25.840 --> 27:28.172
Oh, come on.

27:28.210 --> 27:29.939
Where's the
old Will?

27:29.980 --> 27:31.948
Embrace
the risk.

27:31.980 --> 27:33.777
No, thanks.

27:33.820 --> 27:35.173
Wuss.

27:35.220 --> 27:36.972
(laughs)

27:37.020 --> 27:40.046
Too bad,
you would have won.

27:52.030 --> 27:54.294
(door opens)

27:54.340 --> 27:55.693
Anything?

27:56.740 --> 28:00.130
They want to pay $500,000,

28:00.170 --> 28:02.832
but they're willing
to go to $10 million.

28:02.880 --> 28:04.347
(chuckles)
You're kidding?

28:04.380 --> 28:05.142
Nope.

28:05.180 --> 28:07.944
We were willing to
take $5 million.

28:07.980 --> 28:11.814
(chuckles)

28:11.850 --> 28:14.387
The only bad news is,
I don't think she planted

28:14.420 --> 28:15.853
the story with Gretchen,

28:15.890 --> 28:17.983
but I can't tell.

28:18.030 --> 28:20.453
She's a good bluffer.

28:20.490 --> 28:21.923
Anything else?

28:21.960 --> 28:25.191
Yeah, she's gonna try
to play you.

28:25.230 --> 28:26.891
In what way?

28:26.930 --> 28:28.989
Jealousy.

28:29.040 --> 28:31.008
Using your past?

28:31.040 --> 28:32.905
To what end?
Rattle you,

28:32.940 --> 28:35.272
get you to admit the bottom line
just for the kick of it.

28:35.310 --> 28:38.006
(chuckles)

28:38.050 --> 28:39.199
So you and her, huh?

28:39.250 --> 28:41.912
Two years.

28:41.950 --> 28:43.076
I just don't see it.

28:43.120 --> 28:44.280
I was a different person.

28:44.320 --> 28:45.287
And she's
the same?

28:45.320 --> 28:47.447
Oh, yeah.

28:47.490 --> 28:49.481
Well...

28:53.490 --> 28:57.494
What if I play jealous...

28:58.930 --> 29:00.932
