29:04.340 --> 29:06.308
Maybe you should.

29:06.340 --> 29:08.331
(chuckles)

29:23.160 --> 29:25.424
Tantric sex.

29:25.460 --> 29:26.825
No, sex sex.

29:26.860 --> 29:29.829
No, no, tantric sex.

29:29.860 --> 29:32.021
