of ecstasy.

29:33.900 --> 29:36.391
No, can't we have a
little frictional orgasm?

29:36.440 --> 29:39.830
We don't touch,
we don't undress.

29:39.870 --> 29:41.030
We talk
about our childhoods,

29:41.080 --> 29:43.071
anything but sex.

29:43.110 --> 29:47.342
Delaying gratification
is to increase gratification.

29:47.380 --> 29:50.042
Yeah, but I've spent the last
three hours doing laundry,

29:50.080 --> 29:52.310
and the kids are gonna be
home in a couple of hours,

29:52.350 --> 29:55.854
so I don't really have time
for delayed gratification.

29:55.890 --> 29:56.982
(door opens)

29:57.020 --> 29:58.419
They're home early.

29:58.460 --> 30:00.451
(door closes)

30:01.530 --> 30:03.054
Oh, Owen.

30:03.100 --> 30:05.125
Hello. What a surprise.

30:05.170 --> 30:06.364
Uh, how are you?

30:06.400 --> 30:09.437
Jackie, how... funny.

30:09.470 --> 30:11.938
Yes, so Peter asked me
to pick up Zach and Grace.

30:11.970 --> 30:14.370
I hope you don't mind,
I have my old key.

30:14.410 --> 30:16.571
Oh, hello.

30:16.610 --> 30:19.841
Hello.

30:19.880 --> 30:21.017
My name is Finn.

30:21.050 --> 30:23.109
Uh, Finn's a friend
of mine from school.

30:23.150 --> 30:24.981
Jackie, you're
a little early.

30:25.020 --> 30:26.317
Yes, well, I thought
I'd clean up.

30:26.350 --> 30:28.113
It always gets
so messy here.

30:28.160 --> 30:30.219
But, um, why don't
I come back later?

30:30.260 --> 30:34.094
No, no, sit down,
talk with us.

30:34.130 --> 30:36.394
_You must have
incredible stories

30:36.430 --> 30:38.091
to tell about
your life.

30:38.130 --> 30:39.358
Finn, Jackie's early.

30:39.400 --> 30:40.196
She needs to go.

30:40.230 --> 30:43.199
No, no, thi-this is
a perfect moment

30:43.240 --> 30:46.403
for us to learn
about her past.

30:46.440 --> 30:48.635
Tell us about
your childhood.

30:48.680 --> 30:49.635
JACKIE:
My childhood?

30:49.680 --> 30:50.635
FINN:
Yes.

30:50.680 --> 30:52.147
JACKIE:
Where should I start?

30:52.180 --> 30:54.614
Chicago was very different
when I was a girl.

30:54.650 --> 30:55.969
