30:59.990 --> 31:01.651
I have to go.

31:01.690 --> 31:03.180
Good-bye.

31:03.220 --> 31:04.881
Kids?

31:04.930 --> 31:06.386
Boy and girl.

31:06.430 --> 31:08.318
You think
this mediation is hard?

31:08.360 --> 31:09.349
(chuckles)

31:09.400 --> 31:11.868
I'm really sorry
about all of this.

31:13.300 --> 31:15.268
Hey, they're all tough.

31:15.300 --> 31:17.165
We just have
to remain human.

31:17.200 --> 31:19.600
How do we do that?

31:19.640 --> 31:21.369
Find a box for this

31:21.410 --> 31:24.208
and keep it in that box.

31:25.250 --> 31:27.309
Thank you.

31:27.350 --> 31:30.171
