31:30.220 --> 31:32.188
We are not paying a cent
above her medical bills.

31:32.220 --> 31:33.687
Then let's go to court.

31:33.720 --> 31:35.210
You failed, Will.
I don't have
to put up with this.

31:35.260 --> 31:36.318
Just face the fact.

31:36.360 --> 31:37.315
Okay, stop.

31:37.360 --> 31:38.156
How did I...?

31:38.190 --> 31:39.521
The point of bringing
you two together

31:39.560 --> 31:41.198
