34:38.270 --> 34:40.568
Mr. Gardner's bringing
this issue up again,

34:40.610 --> 34:42.737
so I had a study done

34:42.780 --> 34:46.170
by the respected Benzor Labs
in Quantico, Virginia.

34:47.210 --> 34:49.269
