36:51.440 --> 36:52.839
Oh, my God.
Yeah.

36:52.870 --> 36:54.679
It's wonderful, isn't it?

36:54.710 --> 36:56.439
People love humility.

36:56.480 --> 36:58.471
Tony Hayward needed
a pie in the face.

36:58.510 --> 36:59.306
