37:13.890 --> 37:15.391
I'm good at my job, Diane,

37:15.430 --> 37:17.398
but I can't have leakers.

37:17.430 --> 37:19.489
It's unprofessional.

37:19.530 --> 37:22.294
Will didn't leak.

37:26.340 --> 37:28.331
(crowd chatter,
piano music playing)

37:31.510 --> 37:33.341
So you're here to give up.

37:33.380 --> 37:37.510
Ten million, and we
won't accept a penny less.

37:37.550 --> 37:39.586
Really? (laughs)

37:39.620 --> 37:41.588
You and your lawyer friend
cook something up?

37:41.620 --> 37:44.453
It didn't work for you
to blame the painkiller.

37:44.490 --> 37:46.287
It didn't work for you
to blame the victim,

37:46.330 --> 37:47.456
so minor modification.

37:47.490 --> 37:49.526
That's what your
case rests on now.

37:49.560 --> 37:52.825
Dr. Farland's SCS is
merely a minor modification

37:52.870 --> 37:54.531
of existing SCSs.

37:54.570 --> 37:56.834
Have some pastrami, Will.

37:56.870 --> 37:59.839
Let's leave all this boring
medical talk behind.

37:59.870 --> 38:04.375
The problem is, medicine
is a lot like politics.

38:04.410 --> 38:07.379
And all we had to do
was follow the money.

38:07.410 --> 38:09.378
She never was jealous,
was she?

38:09.420 --> 38:10.773
Your lawyer friend.

38:10.820 --> 38:12.685
That was all a piece
of playacting?

38:12.720 --> 38:15.450
Dr. Farland, your
man of healing,

38:15.490 --> 38:17.981
invented an SCS
to make money.

38:18.020 --> 38:21.285
30% on every
device implanted.

38:25.600 --> 38:27.898
Oh. Sorry. Sorry.

38:27.930 --> 38:29.090
Who was that?

38:29.140 --> 38:30.562
Kalinda.

38:30.600 --> 38:31.601
Here's a copy for you.

38:31.640 --> 38:32.766
What is this?

38:32.810 --> 38:34.539
Farland's patent
application.

38:35.580 --> 38:36.979
Yeah, I know.

38:37.010 --> 38:38.546
It's a good
read, though.

38:38.580 --> 38:40.104
The problem for you is,

38:40.150 --> 38:42.710
Dr. Farl_and had to insist
on its originality.

38:42.750 --> 38:44.115
I get it.

38:44.150 --> 38:45.947
You don't have
to lord it over me.

38:45.990 --> 38:49.118
No, I won, so you
have to listen.

38:49.160 --> 38:51.583
Dr. Farland had to
insist on the originality

38:51.630 --> 38:53.723
of his device to
file a patent.

38:53.760 --> 38:57.491
"This SCS is a truly
original development

38:57.530 --> 38:59.122
"_in severe back
pain management.

38:59.170 --> 39:00.865
It is not a_ mere
modification..."

39:00.900 --> 39:03.368
How nice of him to
use those words.

39:03.400 --> 39:04.958
"...of existing
SCSs on the market.

39:05.010 --> 39:07.001
Therefore,
patent. . ."
I can read.

39:07.040 --> 39:10.532
You're not going to be
a sore loser, are you?

39:10.580 --> 39:13.048
Eight million dollars.

39:13.080 --> 39:14.638
Ten. By today.

39:14.680 --> 39:16.113
(laughing):
No.

39:16.150 --> 39:18.710
Eight. That's more
than you thought you'd get.

39:18.750 --> 39:20.581
I'll talk to my client.

39:20.620 --> 39:23.111
I need a new home.

39:25.630 --> 39:27.552
You need a...?
New home.

39:27.590 --> 39:29.990
My firm is going under.

39:30.030 --> 39:32.089
Monty & Columbech?

39:32.130 --> 39:33.859
Breaking up.

39:33.900 --> 39:36.391
Litigation's going one way,
acquisitions another.

39:36.440 --> 39:38.658
How many in litigation?
Me.

39:38.710 --> 39:41.508
Eight other top-flight lavwers.

39:41.540 --> 39:43.030
We need a home.

39:43.080 --> 39:45.378
I'll check with Diane.

39:47.750 --> 39:49.741
I miss you.

39:54.590 --> 39:57.184
Ira? Hey.

39:57.220 --> 39:59.484
So, it looks like
we'll make a deal.

39:59.530 --> 40:00.622
I heard.

40:00.660 --> 40:03.754
I just wanted to thank you
for all of your hard work.

40:03.800 --> 40:05.597
You don't have to thank me.

40:05.630 --> 40:07.518
I wasn't the one
who played them.

40:07.570 --> 40:09.197
We...

40:09.240 --> 40:11.196
That's not
why we won.

40:11.240 --> 40:12.867
You won because of the facts.

40:12.910 --> 40:16.698
You got your client rich because
you played them... and me.

40:16.740 --> 40:18.879
That's not fair.

40:18.910 --> 40:20.446
It i fair.

40:20.480 --> 40:23.938
It may not be polite,
but it is fair.

40:23.980 --> 40:25.948
Don't worry about it.

40:25.990 --> 40:29.778
IfI needed a lawyer,
I'd probably hire you, too.

40:29.820 --> 40:31.856
Very nice to meet you.

40:39.200 --> 40:41.225
Hey, Mom.

40:41.270 --> 40:43.659
Just wanted to see
how you were d0ing.

40:44.710 --> 40:46.666
How's your thing?

40:46.710 --> 40:48.575
It was good.

40:48.610 --> 40:51.477
I don't know.

40:51.510 --> 40:53.569
I go back and forth
on work.
Yeah.

40:53.610 --> 40:55.578
Same with Dad.

40:57.180 --> 40:58.818
I want to do something
very old-fashioned.

40:58.850 --> 41:00.715
I want to kiss you
on the forehead.

41:00.750 --> 41:01.887
Is that all right?

41:01.920 --> 41:03.888
(laughs)
Sure.

41:08.560 --> 41:11.495
Tucking in is too much.

41:11.530 --> 41:13.498
Right.

41:13.530 --> 41:15.532
Sorry.

41:17.770 --> 41:19.761
Love you.

41:28.110 --> 41:30.146
(sighs)

41:30.180 --> 41:31.818
I'm getting boring.

41:31.850 --> 41:33.681
Getting?

41:33.720 --> 41:35.859
I'm serious.

41:35.890 --> 41:39.257
I used to be... interesting.

41:39.290 --> 41:41.827
I spent the entire day

41:41.860 --> 41:44.863
doing laundry
and watching daytime TV.

41:44.900 --> 41:46.026
I saw the clothes.

41:46.070 --> 41:47.560
Thank you.

41:47.600 --> 41:48.828
I mean, when did this happen?

41:48.870 --> 41:51.134
You're the one out having sex
with your boyfriend.

41:51.170 --> 41:52.660
Owen...

41:52.710 --> 41:54.632
And I'm the one
at home with the kids.

41:54.680 --> 41:57.501
And it's much
appreciated.

41:58.750 --> 42:01.548
Are you gonna get hurt
by this guy?

42:03.180 --> 42:05.740
I don't know.

42:05.790 --> 42:08.657
I have no perspective.

42:08.690 --> 42:10.681
You should have rebelled
in high school.

42:10.720 --> 42:12.688
Then you wouldn't
have to do it now.

42:12.730 --> 42:15.255
Is that what this
is, rebellion?

42:15.300 --> 42:18.690
Or love.

42:18.730 --> 42:20.789
It's not love, is it?

42:22.140 --> 42:24.335
No.

42:24.370 --> 42:26.668
Good.

42:26.710 --> 42:30.737
'Cause that would make it
very complicated.

42:30.780 --> 42:34.773
Mmm.
(sighs)

